<html>
<head>
    <title>Editing {{ event.name }} - EveMapp WebManager</title>
    {% stylesheets '@ManagerBundle/Resources/less/editor/*' filter='cssrewrite' %}
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="{{ asset_url }}"/>
    {% endstylesheets %}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('bundles/manager/css/jquery.datetimepicker.css') }}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.4/themes/smoothness/jquery-ui.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://js.arcgis.com/3.9/js/esri/css/esri.css">

    <script src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/js/jquery-1.10.2.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/js/jquery-ui-1.10.4.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/js/jquery.datetimepicker.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="http://malsup.github.io/jquery.form.js"></script>
    <script src="http://js.arcgis.com/3.9/"></script>


    <script src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/js/event/editor_ui.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/js/event/editor.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/js/event/editor_ui_object.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/js/event/editor_ui_entry.js') }}"></script>


</head>
</html>
<body>
<div id="container">

    <div id="map"></div>
    <div id="toolbar">


        <div id="infoToolButton" class="toolButton tooltipAble" data-tool="info" data-tooltip="Info and Edit tool">
            <img src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/images/symbols/info.png') }}"/>
        </div>
        <div id="dragToolButton" class="toolButton tooltipAble" data-tool="drag" data-tooltip="Drag objects">
            <img src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/images/symbols/move.png') }}"/>
        </div>
        <div id="createToolButton" class="toolButton tooltipAble" data-tool="create" data-tooltip="Create new objects!">
            <img src="http://placehold.it/100x100"/>
        </div>
        <div id="deleteToolButton" class="toolButton tooltipAble" data-tool="delete" data-tooltip="Delete objects">
            <img src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/images/symbols/delete.png') }}"/>
        </div>
        <div id="heatMapToolButton" class="toolButton tooltipAble" data-tool="heatMap"
             data-tooltip="View the heatmap of your event!">
            <img src="http://placehold.it/100x100"/>
        </div>


        <div id="toolWindow">
            <div class="toolExplanation">
                <h3>Welcome to EveMapp</h3>

                <p>
                    Using EveMapp for your event has been the right choice, as you will know soon! You are
                    looking at the map builder for our mobile application. With this you can mold the entire event area
                    to your great vision.
                </p>

                <p>
                    To use it select a tool above. Every tool will supply you with an explanation of how it works, but
                    it's
                    pretty simple! Also keep in mind, that everything is immediately saved to our servers, so you don't
                    have to worry about that!
                </p>

                <p>
                    We wish you the best of luck with organizing your event!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="infoTooltip" style="display: none;"></div>
    </div>

</div>
</div>
<div id="overlay">
    <div id="overlay_content">
        <div id="loading_image"><img src="{{ asset('bundles/manager/images/loading1.gif') }}"/></div>
        <div id="content_message" class="overlay_message"></div>
        <div id="loading_message" class="overlay_message">Loading Map...</div>
        <div id="error_message" class="overlay_message"></div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>